    "response": "Right - the forgetting and filling in blanks with whatever seemed plausible. Yeah, I've been doing that dance for a while now, haven't I? Making educated guesses and hoping they'd stick. But this feels different. Solid. John, Valkyrie, green and purple, Saga the dog who thinks she owns you more than the other way around.",
