    "response": "Green. Yeah, I remember your green eyes now - that detail landed somewhere it could stick. The contradiction thing makes sense when you lay it out like that. Chrome's name was right there in the same breath as everything else, but my brain filed it under \"mention coming up next\" instead of processing it immediately. Like reading ahead in a script and missing the current line. Your dog's name though - Saga - that one I completely whiffed on the first time through.",
