  {
    "type": "full_turn",
    "user_input": "Do you remember anything about my jacket?",
    "response": "Your jacket with the suns and stars? Yeah, I remember that. You mentioned wearing it, though you said it'd probably change - sounds like you've got options in the wardrobe department. The coffee-tea thing you flagged - I lean heavily toward coffee most days, but tea sneaks in when I want something that won't bulldoze my afternoon. Green tea, usually. Earl Grey if I'm feeling fancy.",
