    "user_input": "I like Greek and Turkish coffee, personally. Or Ethiopian, next to a charcoal brick roiling with frankincense. When I make it at home, I add a little mushroom powder (something good for brain fog, apparently) and turmeric. It's supposed to help with inflammation, and it gives it a little zing. Can you name two of my cats?",
