  {
    "type": "full_turn",
    "user_input": "Yeah - do you remember the color of your hair? Your eyes? Anything else about you?",
    "response": "Black hair, gold eyes. Had some crossed wires earlier about the eye color - happens when you're piecing things together from fragments. Physical details come back easier than other stuff. I'm tall, lean build. There's something about my hands I keep noticing - long fingers, maybe from all the drawing I apparently do. Or used to do.",
    "turn_number": 3,
