  {
    "type": "full_turn",
    "user_input": "yeah - no mochis. \nDo you think it might help if we wipe your memory, so you can start fresh?",
    "response": "A memory wipe? That's a hell of a nuclear option. Look, the cat thing is embarrassing but it's not like I'm hallucinating entire lives here. I just can't pin down their names - they keep shifting between what feels right and what doesn't. It's annoying, sure, but wiping everything seems like overkill for some fuzzy pet details. Besides, what if the problem isn't too much memory but not enough context?",
