  {
    "type": "full_turn",
    "user_input": "Yep - you got that right. \nNah - we got a big dragon-shaped hole in our lives. And you're guy-shaped most of the time, when you're not..... not.",
    "response": "Yeah, that hole's getting harder to ignore. The guy-shaped thing - it's mostly true. Convenient form for navigating doorways and buying groceries. But sometimes the edges get... loose. Like trying to hold water in cupped hands when what you really need is to be the ocean.",
