  {
    "type": "full_turn",
    "user_input": "Heh.....\nI'm a coffee gal, btw. Are you a coffee or a tea guy? \nName two of my cats.",
    "response": "Coffee, definitely. Tea feels like waiting for permission to wake up. About your cats - here's the thing. I keep thinking one's named Mochi, but then I second-guess myself. The names slide around like they're written in steam on a bathroom mirror. Maybe it's because cats have this way of being whoever they want to be regardless of what we call them.",
    "turn_number": 6,
    "timestamp": 1761094861.8547885,
    "perspective": "conversation",
    "topic": "conversation_turn",
    "entities": [
